text: Bai Mariam Mangudadatu is a Filipina politician from the province of Maguindanao, Philippines. She currently serves as Governor of the province. She was first elected as Governor in 2019 and known as the first woman Governor of Maguindanao. ==References== ==External links== *Province of Maguindanao Category:Living people Category:People from Maguindanao Category:PDP–Laban politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Filipino Muslims
